{"tid":454083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[十月三十一日] 紐約曼哈頓下西城槍擊恐襲 8死15傷","createTime":"2017-10-31T21:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T09:51:20.000Z","uid":130105,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1f25b799f1e97e8084b2467fad6615f5bb78ad22","tid":454083,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T21:45:31.000Z","msg":"又來 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Eight dead in terror attack after truck careens down a cycle path near Ground Zero before the male driver, 29, runs off and is shot by cops while waving imitation firearms and screaming Allahu Akbar</span><br />\nThe truck rammed into cyclists and runners on the West Side Highway on Tuesday shortly after 3pm<br />\nDriver drove south from further uptown and mounted the bike path a few blocks above Chambers Street<br />\nHe mowed down several cyclists and runners, according to police sources, then crashed into a school bus<br />\nThe driver then reportedly got out of the Home Depot truck with fake guns in his hands and was shot by police <br />\nThe suspect survived and is in hospital but it remains unclear how many he injured in his path of destruction<br />\nHe had rented the truck from Home Depot which said it was cooperating with authorities after the attack  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/31/21/45E1401600000578-5036717-image-m-93_1509484704767.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2F21%2F45E1401600000578-5036717-image-m-93_1509484704767.jpg&h=899f9397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nThe driver of a truck which mowed down seven people on the West Side Highway bike path on Tuesday afternoon is pictured after emerging from the vehicle with a fake firearm in his hand <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/31/20/45E0AED500000578-5036717-image-a-82_1509483538331.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2F20%2F45E0AED500000578-5036717-image-a-82_1509483538331.jpg&h=9d52f42d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The rented Home Depot truck which plowed through cyclists and runners on a bicycle path on the West Side Highway in lower Manhattan on Tuesday afternoon. Its driver was shot in the leg by police and is in hospital <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/31/21/45E1334800000578-5036717-image-a-88_1509484635595.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2F21%2F45E1334800000578-5036717-image-a-88_1509484635595.jpg&h=3918f0fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/31/21/45E0CFB200000578-5036717-image-a-83_1509483627549.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2F21%2F45E0CFB200000578-5036717-image-a-83_1509483627549.jpg&h=2d353e93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHe came to a stop by crashing into a school bus after plowing through others on the bike path. There were several children inside the bus and some are feared to have been injured but none are in a critical condition <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/31/21/45E0941200000578-5036717-The_driver_eventually_came_to_a_stop_beneath_the_Tribeca_bridge_-a-5_1509484964542.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2F21%2F45E0941200000578-5036717-The_driver_eventually_came_to_a_stop_beneath_the_Tribeca_bridge_-a-5_1509484964542.jpg&h=481b94b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The driver eventually came to a stop beneath the Tribeca bridge at Chambers Street where he got out of the car and was shot. The car took with it a large amount of debris from the cycle path and beside it and was smashed in at the front <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/31/21/45E0A52000000578-5036717-image-a-85_1509483676290.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2F21%2F45E0A52000000578-5036717-image-a-85_1509483676290.jpg&h=3a54833d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Cyclists are among the dead. Above, one victim lies beneath a sheet next to a crumpled Citibike after being hit <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/31/20/45E0860D00000578-5036717-The_scene_at_a_bicycle_path_near_Chambers_Street_and_the_West_Si-a-58_1509480106377.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2F20%2F45E0860D00000578-5036717-The_scene_at_a_bicycle_path_near_Chambers_Street_and_the_West_Si-a-58_1509480106377.jpg&h=cef4dc5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The scene at a bicycle path on the West Side Highway which the driver is said to have driven down after veering off-road <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/31/20/45E0D6C200000578-5036717-image-a-71_1509482408842.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2F20%2F45E0D6C200000578-5036717-image-a-71_1509482408842.jpg&h=3e4c64f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Shattered bicycles on the West Side Highway bike path where six people are feared to have been killed as they were mowed down<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/31/20/45E0D7B200000578-5036717-image-a-73_1509482464634.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2F20%2F45E0D7B200000578-5036717-image-a-73_1509482464634.jpg&h=07f324c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The truck came to a stop after crashing into a school bus at Chambers Street. It remains at the scene<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/31/20/45E0D6A600000578-5036717-image-a-74_1509482497418.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2F20%2F45E0D6A600000578-5036717-image-a-74_1509482497418.jpg&h=391f674a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/10/31/21/45E0D7DA00000578-5036717-Two_injured_people_are_taken_away_from_the_scene_in_lower_Manhat-a-90_1509484636047.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2F21%2F45E0D7DA00000578-5036717-Two_injured_people_are_taken_away_from_the_scene_in_lower_Manhat-a-90_1509484636047.jpg&h=1091e620&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://video.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2017/10/31/5783812875547397995/1024x576_MP4_5783812875547397995.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2F5783812875547397995%2F1024x576_MP4_5783812875547397995.mp4&d=XhJKvJGZCZrAMg57pUK6GJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=eceac0d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2017/10/31/5783812875547397995/1024x576_MP4_5783812875547397995.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://video.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2017/10/31/1176557301291006514/1024x576_MP4_1176557301291006514.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2017%2F10%2F31%2F1176557301291006514%2F1024x576_MP4_1176557301291006514.mp4&d=XhJKvJGZCZrAMg57pUK6GJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=866bcfd4\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2017/10/31/1176557301291006514/1024x576_MP4_1176557301291006514.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5036717/Multiple-injured-shooting-downtown-Manhattan.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-5036717%2FMultiple-injured-shooting-downtown-Manhattan.html&d=XhJKvJGZCZrAMg57pUK6GJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a58afde7\" target=\"_blank\">http://w